          Location and Hours

          The National Gallery of Art and Sculpture Garden, located between 3rd
          and 9th Streets at Constitution Avenue, NW, is open Monday through
          Saturday from 10 a.m. to 5 p.m and Sunday from 11 a.m. to 6 p.m. The
          Gallery is closed on December 25 and January 1.

